Metadata.Title: Unstaffed, Part 1
Metadata.Description: Good morning 47, this contract is a bit of a big one. These staff members are part of an mafia called "The Staffers" and are notorious for murdering and framing customers of various high profile hotels. Our Contracter, Marrie is a large hotel chain that stands to lose a lot if The Staffers continue to sneak into their hotels.You must kill all hotel staff, if even one is left they will only cause more trouble in the future. As a bonus, try killing your targets with an axe, we're trying to frame this on a famous axe murder that did a number of murder at this hotel some years ago.  (PS I realize the first contract was missing some targets so now it should be fixed)
